  "id": "RAW_12766865",
  "title": "五位硅谷创始人：如果 2026 年从 0 开始创业，建议这么做 丨 Silicon Valley Girl",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk5MDkxNDU4Nw==&mid=2247485203&idx=1&sn=3f276f1fe658180a2e5c486e85f23f3c",
  "date": "2026-01-15 14:42:00",
  "author": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "siteName": "晚点再听LaterCast",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ece76f27&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FaubJvugmGm1xGQ6GJbZmpgl0faMvS0wpiam6GQUUBaMEAxeq7BQHxhQOGIiaWjic5qriaAgLw6cTRtcxKXxA5Ld9cg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:14px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">我们每天为你更新硅谷最新的 AI 创业与科技播客总结，让你与前沿保持同频。全文约 3500 字，如果你现在没有时间，试试转成播客稍后再听</span><a class=\"weapp_text_link js_weapp_entry\" style=\"\" data-unique-id=\"mkfk4r0j-pe68hp\" data-miniprogram-type=\"text\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wxa4c5894e8895e7d1\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/podcast-list/podcast-list\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"晚点再听LaterCast\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-applink=\"#小程序://晚点再听/wH0V6wuIghALSus\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">晚点再听LaterCast</span></a></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">“唯一的赌注是赌你自己的痴迷，而不是赌市场时机或竞争对手。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">“不要问用户‘喜不喜欢’，要问他们‘这值多少钱’。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:30px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\">“普通人在困难的第六个小时放弃，赢家会再坚持两天。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果明天你失去了一切，你的钱、你的人脉、你的声誉，只剩下一台电脑和互联网连接，而时间来到了 2026 年。在这个 AI 工具普及、技术不再是壁垒的时代，你要如何从零开始，重新建立一家能够盈利的企业？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是是主持人向五位创始人提出的考题。他们中有管理着十亿美元估值独角兽的 CEO，也有连续创业成功的实战派。他们的答案几乎一致：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">不要去追逐风口，不要试图做一个面面俱到的“全能选手”，更不要在第一天就想着颠覆世界。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个 AI 让“一个人活成一支队伍”成为可能的年代，技术门槛被拉平，意味着竞争回归到了最本质的层面：你是谁？你解决了什么真问题？你有多痴迷？本期长文将拆解这五位创始人的真实经验。从寻找个人护城河，到利用 AI 快速验证，再到如何像学徒一样从巨人肩膀上起步。如果你正准备在 2026 年开启一段新的商业旅程，这份路线图或许有所启发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">Vise CEO 的策略：极致长板</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">大多数人在职业生涯初期，总是在试图修补自己的短板。但 Vise 的联合创始人兼 CEO Samir Vasavada 提出了一个相反的观点：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">忘掉你的弱点，全力打磨你的长板。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“找到你在世界上最擅长的那一件事，然后忽略其他所有。大多数人总是从一件事跳到另一件事，但现实是，所有的超额回报都来自于长期坚持做一件事并获得复利。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果一切归零，Samir 的第一步不是去写代码或找投资，而是进行一次残酷的自我审计。他提供了一个非常落地的框架来发现所谓的“超能力”：去问你身边最亲密的朋友。问他们“你为什么愿意和我做朋友？”“你为什么喜欢和我一起工作？”“我最棒的地方是什么？”。这些答案往往会惊人地聚焦在同一个点上，也许你是极佳的沟通者，也许你是天生的销售，又或许你擅长解构复杂的产品逻辑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">找出这个点，然后把自己变成这个领域的世界第一。在 2026 年，平庸的技能会被 AI 瞬间替代，只有在一个细分领域做到极致的“长板”，才是无法被算法抹平的护城河。职业生涯的增长逻辑与资本运作如出一辙，分散投资或许能保本，但只有重仓那个增长最快的资产，才能实现指数级跃迁。对于创业者而言，这个资产就是你不可替代的个人核心竞争力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Opus Clip CEO 的策略：先找“痛苦”，再写代码</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于技术出身的创始人来说，最大的诱惑莫过于拿着锤子找钉子。Opus Clip 的创始人 Young Zhao 坦言，如果重新开始，他会极力克制自己写代码的冲动。</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“第一件事永远是弄清楚什么是真正的痛苦工作。”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Young 的重启计划非常具体：前两到三周，完全不碰键盘，只做一件事——理解。他会通过市场细分，找到一个垂直的利基市场，深入研究目标用户现有的工作流、痛点以及他们正在使用的替代方案。在没有深刻理解用户之前，任何代码都是浪费。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“反馈不应该只是‘你喜欢这个产品吗？’，而应该是‘我为你解决了什么问题？’以及‘你认为这个价值多少钱？’。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">一旦痛点被确认，利用现在的 AI 编程工具，构建一个概念验证原型只需要几天时间。但这仅仅是开始。他强调，在早期就要思考一个常被忽视的问题：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">这一路走来，我能积累什么样的专有数据？</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在 AI 时代，算法和模型可以被轻易复制，但随着用户增长而不断积累、自我增值的专有数据集，才是后期真正的壁垒。哪怕在第一天不需要完美的护城河，但你心中必须要有这张蓝图。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Perplexity CEO 策略：关注你的痴迷</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对 Google 这样看似不可战胜的巨头，Perplexity 的创始人 Aravind Srinivas 杀出了一条血路。他的建议直击那些喜欢过度分析的聪明人：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“别试图做一个在白板上画战略的大师，那毫无意义。”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 AI 领域，资本支出巨大，巨头们盯着每一块可能的增量蛋糕。一旦你的点子被验证可行，他们会毫不犹豫地复制。如果你的赌注是建立在“市场时机”或“竞品分析”上，你注定会输。你唯一能赌的，是你自己的痴迷。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“唯一的赌注是赌你自己的痴迷。因为当所有的困难都堆积如山时，只有那个对问题最痴迷的人才会坚持下去，证明世界是错的。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aravind 认为，要在任何领域达到顶尖水平，至少需要两年的深度沉浸。如果你现在一无所有，最好的策略不是马上创业，而是潜下心来，像苦行僧一样在一个领域深耕。可以去现有的公司做实习生，如果拿不到全职 Offer 就从打杂做起，倾注所有的时间去积累。那种“随便做几个月就能成功”的幻想，在 2026 年的高强度竞争中是不存在的。只有当你对某个问题的理解深度超越了世界上 99% 的人，你的商业直觉才会变得敏锐且精准。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">连续创业家 Daniel Priestley 策略：学徒模式</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于那些充满野心但缺乏经验的 20 岁年轻人，Daniel Priestley 给出了最务实的建议：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">不要急着做 CEO，先去给一位优秀的企业家做“二把手”。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">他提出了一个具体的“7-7-6 学徒模式”：寻找一家年收入达到七位数（百万级）、利润达到六位数（十万级）的企业，并在其创始人身边至少并肩工作六个月。为什么是这个规模？因为如果去了一家年收几十亿的大公司，你只是流水线上的一颗螺丝钉，根本接触不到商业的真实脉搏；而一家年收百万且盈利的公司，正好处于业务跑通但急需扩张的阶段，创始人就在一线，你能直接观察到每一个决策的诞生过程。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“在这个学徒期，你要获取三样东西：自我意识（发现优势与短板）、商业意识（理解如何变现）以及资源获取（接触资金、人才和策略）。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一个价值交换的过程。你带着对新事物（比如 AI）的热情和执行力，去换取创始人二三十年的商业智慧。Daniel 自己在 21 岁创立第一家公司并做到百万营收之前，正是在一位导师手下工作了两年。这种“带薪学习”的机会，能让你在真正独立创业时，避开无数个足以致命的坑。在 2026 年，找到一位愿意带你的“师傅”，比拿到一笔天使投资更珍贵。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit CEO 策略：把“隐性知识”注入 AI</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">Amjad Masad 打造了全球最受欢迎的在线编程环境 Replit，他对 AI 时代的竞争壁垒有着独特的理解。他认为，单纯的知识已经变得廉价，OpenAI 的模型读过所有的书、看过所有的代码。但有一样东西是它们没有的：</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">基于身体体验的隐性知识。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你是 YouTube 领域的专家，你知道什么样的视频节奏能留住观众，这是一种只可意会不可言传的感觉；如果你是一位资深 CFO，你对风险的嗅觉是模型无法通过读取财报学到的。Amjad 的策略是：利用你的领域知识，并通过特定的提示工程，将这些“隐性知识”下载到 AI 代理中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:24px 0px;color:rgb(85, 85, 85);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;padding-left:12px;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:italic;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-left:4px solid rgb(252, 220, 112);font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们每个人在一生中都积累了大量的经验，因为大语言模型没有‘身体’，它们无法获得这些体验。将你的领域知识注入到 Agent 中，那就是你的竞争优势。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不仅仅是技术问题，更是关于“毅力”和“机智”。在 Amjad 看来，在这个工具唾手可得的时代，很多人会在遇到困难的第六个小时选择放弃，而成功者会再坚持一天两天。这种不放弃的劲头，结合独特的领域洞察，是将通用 AI 转化为垂直商业价值的关键。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:40px 0px 20px;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:22px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果我今天重新开始</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">综上所述，如果我在 2026 年从零开始，可行的计划是：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">首先，寻找“创始人-机会契合度”。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;审视我的出身、经历、移民背景，找到那些只有我能讲好的故事，只有我能深刻理解的痛点。这比单纯的 PMF（产品市场契合度）更重要。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">其次，建立一个简单的 AI 内容系统。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;内容是杠杆，也是验证。即便市场看似饱和，但优质内容的增长依然疯狂。我会利用 AI 工具快速产出，建立声量，测试市场反馈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">最后，执行一次 30 天的“发布冲刺”。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;把它当成真正的生意，而不是业余爱好。设定一个清晰的 KPI——是一个付费客户，还是一笔具体的收入？不要凭直觉行事，用数据说话。在这 30 天里，学会聚焦，学会说不，停止无意义的“doom scrolling”（末日刷屏）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:20px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">2026 年，对于那些懂得利用工具、拥有深度认知并愿意从头做起的人来说，依然是最好的时代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">内容来源：“If I Wanted to Build a Business for $0 in 2026, I’d Do This…”丨Silicon Valley Girl</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇集了五位硅谷顶尖创始人的实战建议，探讨在 2026 年 AI 普及背景下，如何通过极致长板、痛点挖掘、个人痴迷、学徒模式及隐性知识构建核心竞争力并从零创业。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇集了五位硅谷顶尖创始人的实战建议，探讨在 2026 年 AI 普及背景下，如何通过极致长板、痛点挖掘、个人痴迷、学徒模式及隐性知识构建核心竞争力并从零创业。",
  "summary": "文章设定了一个 2026 年“归零重启”的创业假设，通过对话 Vise、Opus Clip、Perplexity、Replit 等公司的创始人及连续创业者，总结出一套 AI 时代的创业方法论。核心观点包括：Samir Vasavada 强调通过自我审计发现并重仓“极致长板”；Young Zhao 主张先深入垂直市场理解“痛苦工作”而非急于写代码；Aravind Srinivas 认为在巨头环伺下，唯有对问题的“个人痴迷”能支撑长期复利；Daniel Priestley 建议年轻人通过“7-7-6 学徒模式”积累商业意识；Amjad Masad 则提出将 AI 无法获取的“身体体验与隐性知识”注入 Agent。最后，文章给出了寻找创始人契合度、建立 AI 内容杠杆及 30 天发布冲刺的具体执行路径。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "在 AI 抹平技术门槛的时代，极致的个人长板是唯一的护城河。",
      "explanation": "平庸技能易被 AI 替代，创业者应通过外部反馈识别自己的“超能力”，并将其打磨至世界顶尖，以获得长期复利。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创业应始于对“痛苦工作”的深度理解，而非技术实现。",
      "explanation": "在写代码前应进行数周的市场研究，确认用户愿意为解决该痛点付费，并思考如何积累难以复制的专有数据集。"
    },
    {
      "point": "个人痴迷是应对巨头竞争和创业艰辛的终极赌注。",
      "explanation": "战略和时机易被复制，唯有对特定问题的深度痴迷能支撑创业者在困难时期坚持，并产生超越常人的商业直觉。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过“学徒模式”在盈利的小型企业中快速获取商业实战经验。",
      "explanation": "在年营收百万级的公司担任创始人助手，能直接观察决策过程，获取自我意识、商业意识和资源获取能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将基于身体体验的“隐性知识”注入 AI Agent 以构建竞争优势。",
      "explanation": "LLM 缺乏真实世界的实践感悟，将特定领域的专家经验与提示工程结合，可将通用 AI 转化为高价值的垂直应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "唯一的赌注是赌你自己的痴迷，而不是赌市场时机或竞争对手。",
    "不要问用户'喜不喜欢'，要问他们'这值多少钱'。",
    "普通人在困难的第六个小时放弃，赢家会再坚持两天。",
    "找到你在世界上最擅长的那一件事，然后忽略其他所有。",
    "因为大语言模型没有'身体'，它们无法获得这些体验。将你的领域知识注入到 Agent 中，那就是你的竞争优势。"
  ],
